<p>
    This application allows you to easily generate, view, download, and manage QR codes for various purposes such as Wi-Fi access, emails, phone numbers, and plain text.
</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Create</strong> custom QR codes with category-based formatting.</li>
    <li><strong>View</strong> all generated QR codes in an organized list.</li>
    <li><strong>Search & Filter</strong> your QR codes by name or type.</li>
    <li><strong>Download</strong> individual or multiple QR codes to your device.</li>
    <li><strong>Delete</strong> QR codes selectively or in batches to keep your collection organized.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Use the sidebar to navigate through the app. Your QR codes are stored securely in the database and can be accessed anytime.
</p>

